{"displayTopicName":"Step one for _hashta b’shlucho_","topicTokens":[{"text":"Step one for ","type":"text"},{"type":"italics","tokens":[{"text":"hashta b’shlucho","type":"text"}]}],"paragraphsBySubtopic":{"Step one for hashta b’shlucho":[{"type":"bold","tokens":[{"text":"Step #1:","type":"text"}]},{"text":" Before looking at the text we're going to articulate our expectations about what the Mishnah and Gemara will say. ","type":"text"},{"type":"table_list","alignment":"right","rtl":false,"items":[{"list":false,"hidden":false,"tokens":[{"text":"Let’s do it","type":"local","tokens":[{"text":"Let’s do it","type":"text"}],"targetSubtopic":"Expectations","targetTopic":"Step one for hashta b’shlucho","enclosingTopic":"Step one for hashta b’shlucho","enclosingSubtopic":"Step one for hashta b’shlucho"}]},{"list":false,"hidden":false,"tokens":[{"text":"*Step #2:* Translation","type":"global","tokens":[{"type":"bold","tokens":[{"text":"Step #2:","type":"text"}]},{"text":" Translation","type":"text"}],"pathString":"Step_two_for_hashta_b’shlucho","enclosingTopic":"Step one for hashta b’shlucho","enclosingSubtopic":"Step one for hashta b’shlucho"}]}]}],"Expectations":[{"text":"Okay. First, do you think it works to appoint someone else to do a mitzvah for you? ","type":"text"},{"type":"table_list","alignment":"right","rtl":false,"items":[{"list":false,"hidden":false,"tokens":[{"text":"Let me think","type":"local","tokens":[{"text":"Let me think","type":"text"}],"targetSubtopic":"Expectations-2","targetTopic":"Step one for hashta b’shlucho","enclosingTopic":"Step one for hashta b’shlucho","enclosingSubtopic":"Expectations"}]}]}],"Expectations-2":[{"text":"Good. Assuming it works sometimes, do you think it makes a difference what kind of mitzvah it is? ","type":"text"},{"type":"table_list","alignment":"right","rtl":false,"items":[{"list":false,"hidden":false,"tokens":[{"text":"Let me think","type":"local","tokens":[{"text":"Let me think","type":"text"}],"targetSubtopic":"Expectations-3","targetTopic":"Step one for hashta b’shlucho","enclosingTopic":"Step one for hashta b’shlucho","enclosingSubtopic":"Expectations-2"}]}]}],"Expectations-3":[{"text":"Good. Do you think there's a difference between appointing someone else to to a mitzvah like giving ","type":"text"},{"type":"italics","tokens":[{"text":"tzedukkah","type":"text"}]},{"text":" versus a transaction like buying a house? ","type":"text"},{"type":"table_list","alignment":"right","rtl":false,"items":[{"list":false,"hidden":false,"tokens":[{"text":"Let me think","type":"local","tokens":[{"text":"Let me think","type":"text"}],"targetSubtopic":"Expectations-4","targetTopic":"Step one for hashta b’shlucho","enclosingTopic":"Step one for hashta b’shlucho","enclosingSubtopic":"Expectations-3"}]}]}],"Expectations-4":[{"text":"Good. Do you think someone can become engaged to be married via an appointee? ","type":"text"},{"type":"table_list","alignment":"right","rtl":false,"items":[{"list":false,"hidden":false,"tokens":[{"text":"Let me think","type":"local","tokens":[{"text":"Let me think","type":"text"}],"targetSubtopic":"Expectations-5","targetTopic":"Step one for hashta b’shlucho","enclosingTopic":"Step one for hashta b’shlucho","enclosingSubtopic":"Expectations-4"}]}]}],"Expectations-5":[{"text":"Good. Do you think it makes a difference whether the man uses an appointee to engage the woman or vice versa? ","type":"text"},{"type":"table_list","alignment":"right","rtl":false,"items":[{"list":false,"hidden":false,"tokens":[{"text":"Let me think","type":"local","tokens":[{"text":"Let me think","type":"text"}],"targetSubtopic":"Expectations-6","targetTopic":"Step one for hashta b’shlucho","enclosingTopic":"Step one for hashta b’shlucho","enclosingSubtopic":"Expectations-5"}]}]}],"Expectations-6":[{"text":"Good. Do you think there should be any conditions that might have to be met before using an appointee to get engaged? ","type":"text"},{"type":"table_list","alignment":"right","rtl":false,"items"