r, do you think he has to do it himself, or can he appoint someone to do so? ","type":"text"},{"type":"table_list","alignment":"right","rtl":false,"items":[{"list":false,"hidden":false,"tokens":[{"text":"Let me think","type":"local","tokens":[{"text":"Let me think","type":"text"}],"targetSubtopic":"Expectations-11","targetTopic":"Step one for hashta b’shlucho","enclosingTopic":"Step one for hashta b’shlucho","enclosingSubtopic":"Expectations-10"}]}]}],"Expectations-11":[{"text":"Good. Assuming the father can engage his daughter to someone, should the age of the girl affect whether the father ","type":"text"},{"type":"italics","tokens":[{"text":"should","type":"text"}]},{"text":" do it? ","type":"text"},{"type":"table_list","alignment":"right","rtl":false,"items":[{"list":false,"hidden":false,"tokens":[{"text":"Let me think","type":"local","tokens":[{"text":"Let me think","type":"text"}],"targetSubtopic":"Expectations-12","targetTopic":"Step one for hashta b’shlucho","enclosingTopic":"Step one for hashta b’shlucho","enclosingSubtopic":"Expectations-11"}]}]}],"Expectations-12":[{"text":"Great, those are some of the questions our sugya will address. ","type":"text"},{"type":"table_list","alignment":"right","rtl":false,"items":[{"list":false,"hidden":false,"tokens":[{"text":"Continue to Translation","type":"global","tokens":[{"text":"Continue to Translation","type":"text"}],"pathString":"Step_one_for_hashta_b’shlucho/Step_two_for_hashta_b’shlucho","enclosingTopic":"Step one for hashta b’shlucho","enclosingSubtopic":"Expectations-12"}]}]}]}}